Package com.buschmais.xo.spi.reflection

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AnnotatedElement<AE extends AnnotatedElement>
    Defines a annotated element which provides information about present annotations identified by the annotation types themselves or meta annotations.
    AnnotatedMethod
    Represents an annotated method.
    DependencyResolver.DependencyProvider<T>
    Provides dependencies for an element.
    PropertyMethod
    Defines the interface for property accessor methods (i.e. get/is/set methods).
  • Class Summary

    ClassHelper

    GetPropertyMethod

    SetPropertyMethod
    Represents a set method.
    UserMethod
    Represents a method which cannot be mapped to a property.
